is the murder weapon.

23
00:01:23,220 --> 00:01:24,710
We also got a fingerprint from it.

24
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:26,900
The killer tossed it into the drain

25
00:01:27,470 --> 00:01:28,620
but with the print remained?

26
00:01:28,620 --> 00:01:31,190
We can only say
it's the killer's bad luck.

27
00:01:31,190 --> 00:01:32,620
The drain was an abandoned one.

28
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:33,620
It's very dry inside.

29
00:01:33,620 --> 00:01:35,030
Did you get a match?

30
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:37,500
