The suspect

33
00:01:39,750 --> 00:01:41,470
thought he got away clean

34
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:45,780
by tossing the knife down the drain

35
00:01:45,780 --> 00:01:47,320
without realizing there's a fingerprint.

36
00:01:47,450 --> 00:01:48,000
(Fanfan)

37
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,190
(Improper Relation)
Fanfan said

38
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:51,920
(Lei Wei. Love Rival. Liu Ang)
that Liu Ang and Lei Wei were rivals.

39
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:54,870
Lei Wei pretended not
to know Liu Ang well.

40
00:01:55,620 --> 00:01:57,380
As of now, he is our biggest suspect.

41
00:01:58,820 --> 00:02:00,620
Something about this still feels off.

42
